### <i class="bi bi-file-earmark-bar-graph"></i> Predicting US Skin Cancer Status

<div class="project-summary">
A statistical learning project using 50,000 observations and 50 predictors to classify benign versus malignant skin cancer cases.
</div>

<div class="project-detail">
<strong>Highlights:</strong> compared GLM, LDA, and Random Forest, and selected LDA as the final model based on performance and interpretability.
</div>

